WEBVTT

00:23.090 --> 00:24.590
Do you want a mouthful?

00:25.840 --> 00:26.980
Here you are.

00:30.160 --> 00:32.080
I think I found a way.

01:41.180 --> 01:42.560
Good night.

01:45.440 --> 01:47.700
The wine is mine.

02:12.930 --> 02:14.400
He was a fellow soldier.

02:16.329 --> 02:18.820
We took joint operation three times.

02:19.690 --> 02:22.630
It means…

02:22.630 --> 02:24.520
Means that if you...

02:24.520 --> 02:25.660
Let's not

02:28.140 --> 02:30.160
talk about that.

02:59.950 --> 03:01.460
Drop the gun!

03:06.740 --> 03:08.390
Any troubles? How are you?

03:08.820 --> 03:10.310
What do you think?

03:10.310 --> 03:11.950
Why didn't you tell me

03:11.950 --> 03:13.230
when you would leave and back?

03:13.230 --> 03:15.140
I spent three months in Libya.

03:15.140 --> 03:17.160
and a month in North Uruk with Chengang

03:17.160 --> 03:18.200
Unbelievable!

03:18.200 --> 03:19.690
Why did you go such dangerous places?

03:19.690 --> 03:21.140
This is the most dangerous of all.

03:21.140 --> 03:22.450
My own wife is pointing a gun at me.

03:22.450 --> 03:24.300
It’s the most dangerous.

03:25.270 --> 03:26.980
Did you come back with Chengang?

03:29.890 --> 03:32.770
Chengang has gone home.

03:33.410 --> 03:34.750
When?

03:56.870 --> 04:01.460
Solar power generation doesn't do any harm to the environment

04:01.460 --> 04:04.520
and is a very safe and clean system.

04:04.770 --> 04:07.500
It’s the peace reestablishment program

04:07.500 --> 04:09.290
after the war was over.

04:09.290 --> 04:12.570
The Haesung Group is the leading company

04:12.570 --> 04:15.280
in the field of solar power generation.

04:15.280 --> 04:16.839
It beats Germany

04:16.839 --> 04:18.839
and won the construction rights

04:18.839 --> 04:21.820
-to build the Mouru Power Plant. –Yes.

04:21.820 --> 04:22.910
- Hello. - Hello.

04:22.910 --> 04:24.600
Hi!

04:25.170 --> 04:26.680
When I see a signboard written in Korean

04:26.680 --> 04:28.480
in a foreign country,

04:28.480 --> 04:30.130
I feel a lump in my throat.

04:30.130 --> 04:32.420
Korean all love his country.

04:33.330 --> 04:35.430
Wow. It's so cool.

04:35.430 --> 04:37.220
I want to go up there.

04:38.940 --> 04:40.200
It's something, isn't it?

04:43.420 --> 04:44.170
Mr. Koh.

04:44.170 --> 04:44.730
What is it?

04:44.730 --> 04:46.810
Hello, Manager Jin.

04:47.450 --> 04:49.600
He’s our manager.

04:52.850 --> 04:55.430
I don't work for Haesung.

04:55.430 --> 04:56.659
I'm Mr. Jin,

04:56.659 --> 04:58.570
the chief manager of the Uruk Electric Power Corp.

04:58.570 --> 05:01.390
My full name is Jin Yeong Soo, and my English name...

05:01.390 --> 05:02.970
Jin Yeong Soo?

05:06.880 --> 05:10.410
Richard. Jin Yeong Soo.

05:10.710 --> 05:12.440
Jin Yeong Soo!

05:13.140 --> 05:15.380
Let’s call your Korean name.

05:15.380 --> 05:16.910
Manager Jin.

05:19.240 --> 05:20.750
I don't want you to call me that.

05:20.750 --> 05:21.660
Okay.

05:22.220 --> 05:24.870
I'm not a labor worker

05:24.870 --> 05:26.840
like Mr. Koh here.

05:26.840 --> 05:29.540
I'm an employee of the Uruk Electric Power Corp

05:29.540 --> 05:35.000
and I'm the general manager of this project.

05:35.310 --> 05:35.980
Who's in charge of your team,

05:35.980 --> 05:39.730
who's in a high rank enough to talk to me?

05:39.730 --> 05:42.480
A professor or the team leader? Who’s that.

05:44.370 --> 05:45.470
Let’s go.

05:49.110 --> 05:50.400
No professors?

05:53.159 --> 05:54.900
Hello.

05:54.900 --> 05:57.550
I have good news and bad news.

05:57.550 --> 05:58.760
The good news first.

05:58.760 --> 06:01.120
The lead-poisoned kid?

06:01.120 --> 06:03.010
I know his name. His name is Blacky.

06:03.760 --> 06:06.440
Good.  What's the bad news?

06:06.790 --> 06:08.390
Blacky has disappeared.

06:08.960 --> 06:10.610
What?

06:12.320 --> 06:13.900
When did you see him last?

06:14.620 --> 06:15.570
Nine a.m.

06:15.570 --> 06:17.560
After giving him an IV.

06:17.560 --> 06:20.140
I went to get a snack.

06:20.660 --> 06:23.130
He left this behind.

06:23.130 --> 06:26.390
I think he meant "I'm going home."

06:27.400 --> 06:28.540
Should we go out and look for him?

06:28.540 --> 06:29.920
Are you Tarzan or something?

06:29.920 --> 06:31.850
There’re all mountains, water, and forest outside.

06:31.850 --> 06:32.830
Where can you find him?

06:32.830 --> 06:34.510
So I asked Captain Yoo for help...

06:34.510 --> 06:37.120
Why? No way! Don't even think about it.

06:38.240 --> 06:39.730
He's already here.

06:48.290 --> 06:49.260
Let me see the map.

06:49.760 --> 06:50.510
Here.

06:51.110 --> 06:52.610
This is what Blacky drew.

06:53.470 --> 06:55.100
Blacky drew a map?

06:55.440 --> 06:58.659
Yes. Do you know where it is?

06:59.409 --> 07:02.330
Specter Lemur Woods and Cat Rock next to it.

07:04.010 --> 07:05.420
Blacky is the name of the village.

07:06.310 --> 07:07.280
This village right here.

07:08.140 --> 07:10.880
Blacky was the name of a town?

07:10.880 --> 07:12.500
You couldn't even find out his name?

07:12.960 --> 07:14.170
Clench your teeth.

07:16.430 --> 07:17.600
I'll find him.

07:17.600 --> 07:19.630
I'll find him whatever it takes.

07:20.750 --> 07:22.110
Is it far from here?

07:23.470 --> 07:25.910
They come here to get snacks

07:25.910 --> 07:27.360
and walk for about half a day.

07:29.540 --> 07:30.860
I have an idea.

07:31.340 --> 07:32.990
I want you and  Dr. Song

07:32.990 --> 07:34.170
to take over the power plant.

07:34.170 --> 07:35.260
I'll go find the kid.

07:35.260 --> 07:36.320
By yourself?

07:36.320 --> 07:37.530
Unclench.

07:38.020 --> 07:39.870
I can't do it by myself.

07:39.870 --> 07:41.750
I need someone who knows how to get there.

07:43.530 --> 07:44.630
Do you mind?

07:49.880 --> 07:50.840
We'll leave in 10 minutes.

08:01.120 --> 08:03.040
Keep your eyes on the road.

08:07.550 --> 08:08.910
This is the only road.

08:08.950 --> 08:11.080
You can't miss it.

08:11.760 --> 08:12.860
Good to know.

08:16.460 --> 08:17.740
Did you sleep well last night?

08:17.740 --> 08:19.980
I couldn't, because of you.

08:22.500 --> 08:23.590
About last night...

08:23.590 --> 08:25.430
I'm trying not to talk about it.

08:26.240 --> 08:27.470
Can't you tell?

08:28.780 --> 08:29.930
Why don't you want to talk about it?

08:30.660 --> 08:32.280
I'm a little confused.

08:33.520 --> 08:35.820
Until I clear my head,

08:35.860 --> 08:37.299
I'll avoid the subject.

08:39.960 --> 08:41.900
You can avoid the subject or get mad at me.

08:42.630 --> 08:44.770
But don't think it was a spur-of-the-moment thing.

08:46.240 --> 08:47.180
I hesitated about a thousand times

08:47.180 --> 08:48.370
before I finally did it.

09:08.350 --> 09:09.650
He's over there. That kid.

09:18.620 --> 09:20.490
Once in the morning.

09:24.080 --> 09:26.960
Once in the evening. Okay?

09:26.960 --> 09:29.110
Thank you.

09:30.820 --> 09:32.120
She said thank you, right?

09:33.110 --> 09:34.670
She wouldn't have said,

09:34.670 --> 09:35.730
"get out."

09:41.510 --> 09:43.610
Aren't they the kids who were picking up scrap iron?

09:44.270 --> 09:45.860
You have a good memory.

09:45.860 --> 09:47.870
That's why I don't forget things.

09:48.350 --> 09:49.200
Like what?

09:50.020 --> 09:51.160
Anything.

09:51.710 --> 09:53.980
Please don't try to say

09:53.980 --> 09:55.740
or do things to impress me.

10:07.040 --> 10:08.690
Do all the soldiers here get

10:08.690 --> 10:10.840
top-of-the-line supplies like these?

10:10.840 --> 10:12.390
There’re soldiers from others countries.

10:12.390 --> 10:14.150
To make you not to be surpassed by them,

10:14.150 --> 10:16.690
Korean companies donate these items.

10:16.690 --> 10:19.890
That's so nice of them.

10:20.210 --> 10:24.680
By the way, is Commander Yoon doing okay?

10:25.580 --> 10:26.720
He's fine, sir.

10:28.250 --> 10:30.990
I feel a special connection with Commander Yoon.

10:30.990 --> 10:33.650
I get to have you on foreign soil like this.

10:33.650 --> 10:35.630
Unbelievable.

10:41.960 --> 10:43.920
Excuse me, sir. Can I answer this?

10:43.920 --> 10:44.860
It's rather important.

10:44.860 --> 10:45.530
Sure. Go ahead.

10:45.530 --> 10:46.740
Take it.

10:46.740 --> 10:47.600
Is it Commander Yoon?

10:47.600 --> 10:48.720
It's more important than that.

10:49.350 --> 10:50.230
Bye, sir.

10:51.460 --> 10:52.270
Yes?

10:52.270 --> 10:53.370
Go ahead.

10:53.700 --> 10:55.140
He ate dinner at 19:00,

10:55.140 --> 10:56.620
went to the gym at 20:00 and worked out with his dumbbells

10:56.620 --> 10:59.000
while increasing the weight by 5 kilograms.

10:59.000 --> 11:00.710
He went to his barracks at 21:00,

11:00.710 --> 11:02.150
chatting with his fellow soldiers,

11:02.150 --> 11:04.540
and at 21:30, he went to...

11:06.620 --> 11:07.890
He went where?

11:12.290 --> 11:13.640
At 21:40,

11:14.760 --> 11:15.800
I made eye contact with him.

11:16.350 --> 11:17.300
Really?

11:18.250 --> 11:20.860
I'm so jealous!  What else?

11:21.710 --> 11:24.170
He's walking toward me.

11:24.620 --> 11:27.700
One, two...

11:30.660 --> 11:31.520
What should I do now?

11:31.960 --> 11:32.880
What do you think?

11:33.750 --> 11:36.160
You should hang up. Hang up.

11:37.560 --> 11:40.420
But Lieutenant Yoon is a lieutenant

11:40.420 --> 11:42.670
and you're only a staff sergeant.

11:42.670 --> 11:44.860
When you're exposed by your enemy during espionage,

11:44.860 --> 11:46.190
what's the first thing you do?

11:47.040 --> 11:47.710
Blow myself up?

11:47.710 --> 11:48.820
Listen to the order.

11:48.820 --> 11:49.960
Do as asked. You idiot!

11:50.330 --> 11:51.320
What did I tell you to do?

11:51.670 --> 11:54.930
At least I heard his voice today.

11:56.160 --> 11:57.830
You can hang up now. Thank you.

11:58.470 --> 11:59.860
Thank you. Ma'am!

12:02.480 --> 12:03.390
I'm sorry.

12:03.390 --> 12:04.000
Kim Beom Rae!

12:04.000 --> 12:05.050
Yes, sir!

12:05.050 --> 12:05.960
Laps around the drill grounds

12:05.960 --> 12:06.800
or instant noodles?

12:07.240 --> 12:09.220
I'll cook instant noodles.

12:09.760 --> 12:12.550
Use your sweat instead of water.  Run!

12:13.610 --> 12:15.000
Let me have a shower first, then.

12:18.260 --> 12:21.360
By the way, you have a letter. Sir!

12:35.040 --> 12:37.300
Some really good wine just came in.

12:37.300 --> 12:39.060
Just let me know if you want some.

12:45.150 --> 12:47.370
I can see why you chose this restaurant.

12:47.370 --> 12:49.080
Sergeant Seo was a regular here.

12:49.400 --> 12:51.190
My favorite place is the PX. (POST EXCHANGE)

12:51.670 --> 12:53.460
I love instant food.

12:54.260 --> 12:55.180
I don’t believe you.

12:56.130 --> 12:58.130
Thank you anyway. This is on me.

12:59.720 --> 13:00.440
Okay.

13:03.530 --> 13:05.470
Since it’s my treat,

13:05.470 --> 13:07.090
can I ask you a rather sensitive question?

13:10.320 --> 13:13.220
I've been wondering why did you become a soldier?

13:14.450 --> 13:16.370
Don't tell me it was the uniform reason.

13:19.020 --> 13:20.860
Someone has to do it.

13:26.290 --> 13:27.980
I don't think you like what I do.

13:29.260 --> 13:30.770
That's why you're confused.

13:33.910 --> 13:34.670
You must be really patriotic

13:34.670 --> 13:37.500
to risk your life for your country.

13:37.970 --> 13:39.040
What is patriotism?

13:39.920 --> 13:41.890
You love your country

13:41.890 --> 13:44.010
and are loyal to your nation...

13:44.010 --> 13:45.520
Only soldiers do that?

13:50.290 --> 13:51.110
I don't know

13:51.110 --> 13:53.010
what’s the meaning of patriotism,

13:54.660 --> 13:55.860
but I believe I need to protect children,

13:55.860 --> 13:57.720
beautiful ladies, and senior citizens.

13:58.510 --> 14:01.300
When I meet high school kids smoking on the street,

14:01.300 --> 14:03.730
I’ll raise my courage to say something though I’m scared.

14:04.730 --> 14:06.220
I need to say no to injustice,

14:06.220 --> 14:08.260
even if my life is endangered.

14:08.580 --> 14:12.120
I keep my pride as a soldier.

14:14.460 --> 14:16.310
That's what I believe patriotism is.

14:26.620 --> 14:27.670
Let me ask you something.

14:28.760 --> 14:30.650
If I weren't a soldier

14:30.890 --> 14:32.550
but a mediocre man with rich parents,

14:34.210 --> 14:35.280
would it have been easier between us?

14:37.800 --> 14:41.020
No. I don't like mediocre men.

14:41.510 --> 14:42.510
Right?

14:43.130 --> 14:45.000
I forgot to add

14:45.000 --> 14:46.290
"handsome."

15:01.900 --> 15:03.350
Don't shoot! Don't shoot!

15:03.350 --> 15:05.000
I'm UN. UN.

15:16.920 --> 15:18.090
I paid. Let's go.

15:22.760 --> 15:23.750
Can you find the hardware store

15:23.750 --> 15:24.910
we went to before?

15:25.390 --> 15:26.670
You told me where it is.

15:27.530 --> 15:29.240
Turn at the corner and cross the street.

15:29.830 --> 15:31.040
Right.

15:31.040 --> 15:32.070
You can find it on your own, right?

15:32.070 --> 15:33.190
What's going on?

15:34.160 --> 15:35.570
I need to work in the afternoon.

15:35.570 --> 15:37.360
Then rent a car and go  back.

15:37.890 --> 15:39.360
I'll call the hardware store.

15:39.700 --> 15:41.980
Can I ask what's going on?

15:42.970 --> 15:44.510
I need to go to headquarters.

15:45.320 --> 15:46.400
Thank you for buying me lunch.

15:46.400 --> 15:48.400
Is it about the president of the Arab?

15:48.400 --> 15:49.720
Are you in trouble?

15:50.380 --> 15:52.100
I'm in trouble

15:52.100 --> 15:53.330
because of my report.

15:53.830 --> 15:55.950
We're civil servants during peacetime.

15:55.950 --> 15:57.460
Right.

16:02.730 --> 16:04.280
Let's go. I'll escort you.

16:09.220 --> 16:10.610
Hello?

16:11.740 --> 16:13.350
Ye Hwa!

16:13.820 --> 16:14.760
Anybody?

16:15.380 --> 16:16.520
Oh my!

16:16.520 --> 16:17.740
Doctor Kang?

16:17.740 --> 16:19.240
Captain Yoo called me.

16:19.570 --> 16:21.570
Right. Nice to meet you.

16:21.570 --> 16:22.610
I'm Kang Mo Yeon.

16:22.610 --> 16:24.260
I'm Daniel.

16:24.820 --> 16:27.100
I'm half Korean.  Pardon my awkward pronunciation.

16:27.100 --> 16:30.130
If you find it funny, go ahead and laugh.

16:30.670 --> 16:32.130
Your pronunciation is fine.

16:33.230 --> 16:34.930
Are you a  Dr.?

16:34.930 --> 16:36.950
I do surgery, fix things,

16:36.950 --> 16:38.420
and even deliver calves once in a while

16:38.890 --> 16:40.060
You need a car?

16:49.560 --> 16:51.420
I think we've met before.

16:51.420 --> 16:55.220
You don't seem very surprised.

16:55.220 --> 16:57.340
How is a peacekeeper

16:57.340 --> 16:59.380
threatening an unarmed civilian without a gun?

16:59.380 --> 17:00.510
I shouldn't do that.

17:13.030 --> 17:16.480
Not a civilian. Not unarmed.

17:20.030 --> 17:23.310
I know you have connections with the cops.

17:23.490 --> 17:26.400
Why do you keep showing up near me?

17:37.250 --> 17:39.520
How many times do I have to tell you?

17:41.370 --> 17:42.980
Aim to the back

17:42.980 --> 17:45.100
if you're going to kill a man.

17:46.110 --> 17:49.130
Cops! They're always on the side of money.

17:49.130 --> 17:50.860
Always. Anywhere.

17:53.150 --> 17:54.560
Long time no see, Lieutenant.

17:59.130 --> 18:00.780
I guess you're a captain now.

18:03.150 --> 18:07.310
Captain Argus?

18:08.110 --> 18:09.420
Argus gangs?

18:09.420 --> 18:11.750
Well, let me know if there's any problem.

18:11.750 --> 18:12.690
Okay, bye.

18:14.540 --> 18:17.050
I think the local gang members caused some trouble.

18:17.400 --> 18:18.670
Here are the car keys.

18:18.670 --> 18:19.940
Did anyone get hurt?

18:19.940 --> 18:22.600
If they needed a  Dr., they would've contacted me.

18:23.340 --> 18:24.420
Would you like a cup of tea?

18:24.870 --> 18:26.280
Thank you.

18:33.500 --> 18:37.350
By the way, how do you know Captain Yoo?

18:37.710 --> 18:39.680
Well... That's tough to say.

18:40.160 --> 18:42.200
You could call us "funeral buddies."

18:42.850 --> 18:45.310
In Iraq, in Afghanistan, and even here in Uruk,

18:45.310 --> 18:46.750
we meet each other

18:46.750 --> 18:48.370
at funerals all the time.

18:51.720 --> 18:54.750
I know it's a sensitive question to ask

18:55.600 --> 18:58.630
but I don't think I'll have another chance.

19:00.060 --> 19:03.340
Do you know what Captain Yoo Shi Jin

19:03.340 --> 19:06.300
does exactly?

19:08.470 --> 19:10.330
Lieutenant Yoo Shi Jin!

19:12.080 --> 19:15.820
Serial Number 05-10051.

19:15.820 --> 19:18.560
The Special Warfare Command of the Korean Army.

19:18.560 --> 19:20.610
Lieutenant Yoo Shi Jin!

19:25.240 --> 19:26.840
What's the UN's radio code?

19:27.340 --> 19:29.570
Serial Number 05-10051.

19:29.570 --> 19:30.770
In English!

19:30.770 --> 19:33.280
The Special Warfare Command of the Korean...

19:45.540 --> 19:48.330
Clear!  Lieutenant Yoo is okay.  We're retreating.

19:48.890 --> 19:50.550
There's another soldier in the basement.

19:50.980 --> 19:52.800
I think he's the captain of Delta Team.

19:52.800 --> 19:55.480
We don't have time. There will be a bomb in five minutes.

19:55.480 --> 19:56.750
Since we don't have time, let's hurry up.

20:08.160 --> 20:09.990
The injured soldier's on board.

20:10.480 --> 20:12.270
Get on. Let's go home.

20:33.680 --> 20:34.820
Why are you...

20:34.820 --> 20:36.340
Changed jobs.

20:36.340 --> 20:37.810
As you can see.

20:39.050 --> 20:40.530
Now I can grow my hair out.

20:41.020 --> 20:44.350
Luckily, the jobs are pretty much the same.

20:44.780 --> 20:46.330
Shooting guns

20:46.330 --> 20:47.850
and making money.

20:47.850 --> 20:50.000
What happened to you?

20:50.620 --> 20:53.880
Your code sign is still legendary in Delta Force.

20:53.880 --> 20:55.720
Being a legend doesn't pay.

20:56.280 --> 20:58.470
Listen carefully, Captain!

20:58.470 --> 21:01.180
There are many bad gangs in this neighborhood.

21:01.180 --> 21:03.520
And they have no fear.

21:03.520 --> 21:04.870
No rules. No honor.

21:05.670 --> 21:07.810
They've got no country to serve.

21:12.020 --> 21:13.300
This is your last warning.

21:13.300 --> 21:15.080
Mind your own business.

21:16.810 --> 21:19.100
Even back then and now,

21:19.100 --> 21:20.960
you're far too empathetic.

21:23.530 --> 21:24.830
You're right.

21:25.790 --> 21:28.120
I shouldn't have gone against Allah.

21:29.480 --> 21:34.990
I guess there was a reason why you were dying.

21:34.990 --> 21:37.100
You hide behind your language?

21:37.100 --> 21:38.800
For god's sake!

21:38.800 --> 21:40.310
Piss off!

21:40.770 --> 21:43.390
Don't you dare come near me.

21:44.800 --> 21:46.440
Or else

21:46.910 --> 21:50.320
you're going to have to pay the price.

21:58.960 --> 22:00.060
Anything else you want to know?

22:01.670 --> 22:02.550
No.

22:05.120 --> 22:06.320
That's more than enough.

22:07.780 --> 22:10.210
More than enough for what?

22:10.870 --> 22:11.970
To understand him or

22:13.240 --> 22:15.810
to stay away from him?

23:14.600 --> 23:15.650
Oh my god!

23:16.300 --> 23:17.300
Oh my god!

23:18.310 --> 23:20.610
Hello? Hello?

23:21.420 --> 23:23.000
Captain Yoo!

23:23.000 --> 23:24.340
Doctor Kang. You followed instructions.

23:24.340 --> 23:25.500
You got the car?

23:26.890 --> 23:28.560
Where are you?

23:28.600 --> 23:31.560
I'm done now and I'm going to leave.

23:33.960 --> 23:36.010
Help! Please help!

23:36.370 --> 23:37.330
Where are you?

23:39.650 --> 23:40.580
What do you see?

23:41.110 --> 23:42.360
Tell me what you see now.

23:42.360 --> 23:43.840
Car.

23:43.840 --> 23:45.890
My car is caught at the edge of a cliff.

23:46.310 --> 23:47.490
Can you hear me?

23:47.490 --> 23:49.300
Yes.

23:49.300 --> 23:50.730
Hang in there. I'll be right there.

23:51.620 --> 23:52.590
I'll find you.

24:04.670 --> 24:06.870
Hello? Hello?

24:07.100 --> 24:09.710
Yoo Shi Jin. Don't hang up!

24:14.180 --> 24:17.620
Help me! Anybody?

24:18.320 --> 24:19.650
Please help!

24:24.370 --> 24:25.750
So, mom…

24:25.750 --> 24:28.960
You have a pension plan and a savings account.

24:29.730 --> 24:32.830
Claim them when they mature, okay?

24:34.360 --> 24:37.180
I'm sorry that I said mean things to you.

24:38.410 --> 24:40.360
I love you, mom.

24:40.920 --> 24:44.160
And…

24:46.420 --> 24:49.040
you know the building I signed a contract for?

24:49.040 --> 24:52.360
You have to get the refund.

24:52.680 --> 24:55.800
Say goodbye to Tae Won for me.

24:57.340 --> 25:01.120
I want you two...

25:01.120 --> 25:02.670
This sucks.

25:02.670 --> 25:04.680
Am I going to die like this?

25:20.880 --> 25:21.790
Yoo Shi Jin!

25:21.790 --> 25:23.020
Don't move!

25:23.540 --> 25:24.600
Open the windows!

25:30.290 --> 25:31.290
You can't come to the front seat.

25:31.290 --> 25:33.620
The car's leaning forward! It'll fall.

25:33.620 --> 25:34.880
Lean back as much as you can.

25:36.710 --> 25:38.170
The ground won't hold.

25:39.030 --> 25:40.290
I'm going to let this car go over the cliff.

25:40.290 --> 25:42.580
What? No! Don't!

25:42.580 --> 25:43.510
Look at me!

25:43.790 --> 25:44.670
I can't.

25:44.670 --> 25:46.120
Look at me, Doctor Kang.

25:48.710 --> 25:50.160
Look into my eyes.

25:52.330 --> 25:53.910
Trust me

25:54.650 --> 25:55.940
and hold me tight.

25:58.000 --> 25:59.370
Close your eyes.

26:01.020 --> 26:02.740
I'll save you. I promise.

26:03.850 --> 26:05.040
No.

26:06.800 --> 26:07.750
Take your foot off the brake.

26:07.750 --> 26:09.180
No! I really can't.

26:48.400 --> 26:50.600
Are you okay? Are you hurt?

26:55.010 --> 26:55.950
Cough.

26:56.660 --> 26:57.900
Do you feel any pain?

26:59.560 --> 27:01.180
Yes. I feel pain everywhere.

27:02.680 --> 27:04.420
You crazy!

27:04.420 --> 27:06.790
How could you drop the car off the cliff like that?

27:06.790 --> 27:09.430
You're crazy! Completely crazy!

27:14.470 --> 27:16.430
It's unstable! This is terrible!

27:21.800 --> 27:23.250
I'm okay.

27:24.040 --> 27:24.720
You have enough energy to hit me,

27:24.720 --> 27:26.550
so I think you're okay.

27:27.890 --> 27:28.730
Let's go.

27:29.800 --> 27:32.840
Hold on. I can't get up.

27:33.650 --> 27:35.390
I'm not a soldier.

27:36.310 --> 27:38.250
Do you know how terrified I was?

27:38.730 --> 27:40.550
I thought I was going to die.

27:43.750 --> 27:46.110
I can't let you go off on your own.

27:46.110 --> 27:49.060
I sent you off alone and you ended up hanging off a cliff.

27:50.410 --> 27:51.240
If you take a train alone,

27:51.240 --> 27:52.990
where will you end up?

27:55.480 --> 27:58.740
Stop it! I don't have the energy to laugh.

28:16.640 --> 28:17.730
Sir!

28:18.220 --> 28:19.160
Okay.

28:22.120 --> 28:22.990
Put this on.

28:24.870 --> 28:25.960
I can see thorough your clothes.

28:26.530 --> 28:28.730
Why didn't you give it to me earlier?

28:29.420 --> 28:30.490
I've already seen everything.

28:31.810 --> 28:33.520
I don't want any other guys to see.

28:34.570 --> 28:35.580
Get some rest.

28:38.830 --> 28:39.730
Hey!

28:41.100 --> 28:43.000
Hey!

28:48.850 --> 28:50.190
Who are you?

28:50.190 --> 28:51.700
Where's the boss?

29:04.260 --> 29:05.740
Mansions got a new owner.

29:07.550 --> 29:10.160
But the deal still stays the same.

29:11.650 --> 29:13.180
I don't care.

29:13.500 --> 29:16.290
As long as I get my money.

29:19.950 --> 29:21.280
Here.

29:31.850 --> 29:34.820
Because all Korean men go into the military,

29:37.480 --> 29:39.530
they instantly feel like my brothers.

29:41.450 --> 29:43.120
Next delivery.

29:43.870 --> 29:45.540
Within a week.

29:51.760 --> 29:54.660
But it used to be 10 days.

29:59.300 --> 30:00.760
One week.

30:04.360 --> 30:05.490
Yes.

30:06.030 --> 30:08.510
You crazy idiot!

30:08.510 --> 30:10.900
You don't think I know

30:10.900 --> 30:12.030
where you take your naps?

30:12.030 --> 30:12.790
You idiot.

30:12.790 --> 30:15.970
I won't work overtime. I don't need the money.

30:15.970 --> 30:18.550
Are you the owner of this company?

30:19.190 --> 30:20.540
If you want to do whatever you want,

30:20.540 --> 30:21.920
you quit. You stupid jerk!

30:21.920 --> 30:23.070
Damn.

30:23.070 --> 30:24.680
Just wait and see.

30:24.680 --> 30:25.720
When I go back to Korea,

30:25.720 --> 30:27.380
I'll report you to the labor board.

30:27.420 --> 30:29.560
Mr. Koh! Mr. Koh!

30:29.560 --> 30:30.670
Quick!

30:30.670 --> 30:31.450
Quick!

30:31.450 --> 30:33.390
Safety first! Safety first!

30:33.390 --> 30:34.510
He's here!

30:34.510 --> 30:35.960
That son of a...

30:35.960 --> 30:39.240
Shut your mouth!

30:39.950 --> 30:43.120
Oh my! Thank you, Mr. Jin.

30:43.120 --> 30:44.760
I could've sent an employee.

30:44.760 --> 30:48.390
You didn't have to go to the border

30:48.390 --> 30:50.080
to get the material yourself.

30:50.580 --> 30:52.630
By the way, where's the driver?

30:52.630 --> 30:54.410
Did you drive yourself?

30:59.510 --> 31:01.900
He’s fired today.

31:01.900 --> 31:05.190
Don't worry about it and keep working.

31:05.190 --> 31:07.100
You have a deadline to keep.

31:19.860 --> 31:21.090
Blood?

31:44.390 --> 31:46.950
I brought some coffee. Would you like some?

31:48.090 --> 31:49.110
Pervert!

31:57.810 --> 31:59.240
Your underwear...

32:00.120 --> 32:01.500
the black underwear.

32:01.920 --> 32:03.520
It was navy.

32:04.040 --> 32:05.770
You don't think I knew?

32:07.020 --> 32:07.920
If he didn't become a soldier,

32:07.920 --> 32:10.010
what would he be now?

32:10.690 --> 32:11.580
Is that a question?

32:11.580 --> 32:12.940
I was talking to myself.

32:15.420 --> 32:16.870
If you need a sedative,

32:16.870 --> 32:17.710
let me know.

32:17.710 --> 32:19.510
I'll prescribe you one.

32:20.100 --> 32:22.620
Are you terrified?

32:22.620 --> 32:25.210
I was scared to dead.

32:29.750 --> 32:31.580
Are you worried about me?

32:32.210 --> 32:33.690
I sure am.

32:33.690 --> 32:35.530
You saved my life.

32:37.700 --> 32:38.340
You.

32:38.340 --> 32:40.190
Because I saved your life, now you care about me.

32:44.950 --> 32:46.350
Just now

32:48.940 --> 32:51.880
you risked your life to save me.

32:51.880 --> 32:54.000
Do you know that?

32:56.010 --> 32:57.270
You told me to help you

33:00.060 --> 33:02.840
when we first met.

33:03.280 --> 33:07.630
You had to go through bullets to save your fellow soldier.

33:09.570 --> 33:14.690
The story about Private Ryan.

33:15.690 --> 33:18.650
It wasn't a joke, was it?

33:21.390 --> 33:27.370
So, did you save Private Ryan?

33:34.160 --> 33:35.960
The injured soldier's on board!

33:37.340 --> 33:39.390
Get on! Let's go home!

34:10.760 --> 34:11.900
Please.

34:13.480 --> 34:14.570
Please.

34:21.550 --> 34:24.510
Please hang in there.

34:35.800 --> 34:37.090
I did save him.

34:41.960 --> 34:44.409
What if I did not?

34:45.010 --> 34:47.790
I regretted for the first time today.

34:52.670 --> 34:54.580
When you

34:55.610 --> 34:57.720
sent me to Daniel earlier,

34:58.650 --> 35:00.660
you lied to me, right?

35:01.980 --> 35:03.590
Come to think of it. if you'd gone to headquarters

35:03.590 --> 35:05.800
you couldn't have

35:05.800 --> 35:08.690
come to save me that quickly.

35:09.030 --> 35:13.210
You lied about going to headquarters.

35:14.260 --> 35:16.740
The gunshot I heard.

35:17.580 --> 35:19.690
That was you, right?

35:21.500 --> 35:23.710
I guess it made you feel more complicated.

35:25.400 --> 35:28.180
Can't you just let me handle everything?

35:29.760 --> 35:31.790
This is crazy.

35:32.550 --> 35:34.590
If you do this

35:36.590 --> 35:39.630
it'll make things more complicated.

35:46.620 --> 35:47.830
It's a blackout.

35:47.830 --> 35:49.170
The power supply is unstable here.

35:49.920 --> 35:52.190
It'll come back on in 30 seconds.

36:00.490 --> 36:01.650
If you do anything funny to me in the dark,

36:01.650 --> 36:02.670
I'll scream.

36:08.250 --> 36:10.480
Thank you

36:11.080 --> 36:12.010
for saving my life today.

36:12.010 --> 36:13.300
But still no funny business.

36:15.240 --> 36:18.220
I get it. I give up.

36:33.860 --> 36:36.660
Have you been staring at me like that all along?

36:37.040 --> 36:38.600
Like what?

36:38.600 --> 36:39.960
Penetrating eyes.

36:41.570 --> 36:42.880
You've had your fair share of girls, right?

36:44.330 --> 36:48.240
Pretty girls like funny guys.

36:48.240 --> 36:50.280
Don't you see those soldiers

36:50.280 --> 36:52.490
around me all the time?

36:53.500 --> 36:55.280
You seem to enjoy watching them

36:55.280 --> 36:56.160
running topless every morning.

36:56.160 --> 36:57.820
That's the reason I live here.

36:58.860 --> 37:00.950
Why did I save you?

37:01.590 --> 37:03.950
By the way, what about the car?

37:03.950 --> 37:05.550
I should call the hardware store first.

37:05.550 --> 37:06.770
I already did,

37:07.210 --> 37:10.740
and we'll pull up the car tomorrow.

37:36.410 --> 37:37.420
Why did you have to

37:37.420 --> 37:39.680
let the car fall in the water?

37:40.050 --> 37:41.810
Sorry.  You saved my life.

37:41.810 --> 37:43.990
I'm being selfish.

37:45.380 --> 37:47.200
Don't worry. I'll take care of it.

37:47.200 --> 37:50.220
I'll apologize to him and pay for the car.

37:50.220 --> 37:51.360
Have faith in Daniel.

37:52.730 --> 37:53.880
He can fix anything.

37:54.590 --> 37:55.640
Really?

38:12.900 --> 38:13.940
The walkie-talkies you asked for.

38:13.940 --> 38:15.930
He knows well how to use them.

38:16.510 --> 38:17.600
Why walkie-talkies?

38:17.600 --> 38:20.260
They're more useful than cell phones here.

38:20.260 --> 38:22.330
In case the cell phone doesn't work,

38:22.330 --> 38:23.430
like yesterday.

38:27.080 --> 38:28.340
Thank you.

38:28.340 --> 38:30.680
How much do I owe you?

38:30.680 --> 38:31.620
For these?

38:31.620 --> 38:33.020
No. For the car.

38:34.930 --> 38:36.800
I'll try to fix it first.

38:36.800 --> 38:38.040
Can you fix it?

38:38.270 --> 38:39.800
Even if I do,

38:39.800 --> 38:41.340
it won't be the same.

38:42.400 --> 38:44.310
I could've been nice to her.

38:44.310 --> 38:46.290
I couldn't paint her a nice color

38:46.700 --> 38:47.720
or put expensive gasoline...

38:47.720 --> 38:48.800
The expensive gasoline it likes.

38:48.800 --> 38:49.930
Fighting.

38:51.220 --> 38:52.950
You might not see these walkie-talkies again.

38:53.630 --> 38:54.900
If you have anything to say, now's your chance.

38:59.610 --> 39:01.790
The medical team is channel seven.

39:01.790 --> 39:03.230
You can start using it.

39:03.230 --> 39:04.690
Three is our channel.

39:07.130 --> 39:09.350
When you talk, press this PTT button.

39:09.350 --> 39:10.820
Wait for about one second.

39:13.870 --> 39:15.060
This is Big Boss.

39:15.060 --> 39:16.670
We need medical support, over.

39:17.430 --> 39:18.210
Like this.

39:18.210 --> 39:19.830
Is Big Boss your nickname?

39:19.830 --> 39:22.120
It's a call sign. What about yours?

39:22.410 --> 39:23.510
Well... I don't know.

39:24.130 --> 39:25.670
I…

39:26.160 --> 39:26.970
Pretty Girl?

39:27.900 --> 39:29.170
Please stop.

39:29.170 --> 39:30.120
You look like one.

39:30.120 --> 39:31.150
What?

39:31.720 --> 39:33.840
I'm not a pretty girl, but I look like one?

39:34.650 --> 39:35.240
Sometimes.

39:35.240 --> 39:36.210
Sometimes?

39:36.900 --> 39:37.860
You…

39:38.890 --> 39:40.690
Ah…

39:41.950 --> 39:44.070
Can I interrupt you two lovebirds?

39:46.660 --> 39:47.740
What are you doing here

39:47.740 --> 39:49.240
instead of at headquarters?

39:50.560 --> 39:51.920
I'm here to marry you.

39:52.770 --> 39:55.590
Hey! Don't try to scare me like that!

39:56.080 --> 39:58.300
Did I actually scare Yoo Shi Jin?

40:02.970 --> 40:04.500
I'm here to report, sir!

40:04.500 --> 40:05.780
Lieutenant Yoon Myung Joo was ordered to support

40:05.780 --> 40:07.150
the medical services team

40:07.150 --> 40:08.610
in Company Mouru

40:08.610 --> 40:10.000
on May 28th, 2015.

40:10.000 --> 40:11.380
Therefore, I'm reporting to you.

40:12.110 --> 40:12.900
Sir!

40:15.350 --> 40:16.800
Why do I suspect someone powerful

40:16.800 --> 40:18.980
was behind this transfer?

40:19.570 --> 40:21.760
It's not easy for me to live

40:21.760 --> 40:23.080
with an unjust advantage like this.

40:25.610 --> 40:26.900
I'll let you two talk.

40:29.320 --> 40:31.490
Why don't we say hi to each other?

40:33.510 --> 40:34.560
Let's put everything

40:34.560 --> 40:35.730
behind us and work together.

40:39.330 --> 40:40.390
I have no hands to shake.

40:41.180 --> 40:42.120
I don't want to put things behind us either.

40:52.600 --> 40:54.450
I was wondering.

40:54.800 --> 40:56.390
What's the relationship between you and Doctor Kang?

40:56.720 --> 40:59.390
Did you bump into Mo Yeon accidentally

40:59.390 --> 41:01.540
or have you been seeing each other

41:01.540 --> 41:02.840
and pretended this was a coincidence?

41:04.070 --> 41:04.840
I'm not you.

41:05.530 --> 41:07.210
Besides, show respect to Doctor Kang.

41:07.630 --> 41:08.840
She's your senior at school.

41:08.840 --> 41:09.860
You just knew each other.

41:09.860 --> 41:11.060
How can you side with her?

41:11.060 --> 41:12.170
Don't avoid my question and answer me.

41:12.750 --> 41:13.840
What’s your relationship?

41:14.910 --> 41:16.430
Don't get too close to her..

41:16.970 --> 41:18.290
I don't want her to be my-sister-in-law

41:18.880 --> 41:20.130
What kind of family tree is that?

41:20.740 --> 41:21.960
You said you came here to marry me.

41:21.960 --> 41:24.210
You're right.

41:24.820 --> 41:25.710
Anyway.

41:55.240 --> 41:56.260
Are you alright?

41:57.480 --> 41:58.940
Shh!

42:04.010 --> 42:06.100
Commander Yoon called.

42:06.100 --> 42:07.380
He told me to take good care of you.

42:08.610 --> 42:09.970
Are you going to take good care of me?

42:10.430 --> 42:11.750
I'm going to torture you,

42:11.750 --> 42:13.580
so you can leave voluntarily.

42:14.110 --> 42:15.370
You're only going to be here for a few days.

42:17.160 --> 42:18.810
I heard you're going home early

42:18.810 --> 42:20.390
due to your father's retirement ceremony.

42:21.430 --> 42:23.450
Did Commander Yoon pull some strings?

42:23.450 --> 42:24.500
Strings?

42:24.920 --> 42:26.120
How dare you?

42:28.250 --> 42:30.210
It is consideration, you idiot!

42:31.700 --> 42:33.720
Commander Yoon really likes you.

42:34.890 --> 42:36.350
You'll end up being his son-in-law.

42:36.930 --> 42:38.380
That’s why you should thank me.

42:39.190 --> 42:41.440
You could've been my wife if not for me.

42:42.690 --> 42:44.670
I might just marry you.

42:45.670 --> 42:47.120
Are you threatening me now?

42:50.010 --> 42:51.180
I'm sorry.

42:51.180 --> 42:52.560
I made a mistake.

42:58.790 --> 42:59.920
Have you spoken

43:00.420 --> 43:01.310
to Sergeant Seo?

43:01.310 --> 43:02.160
What do you think?

43:03.540 --> 43:04.810
He's not answering my calls.

43:06.580 --> 43:07.910
He's not answering your calls?

43:08.920 --> 43:10.270
He's answering mine.

43:12.270 --> 43:14.580
He called me a lot.

43:15.810 --> 43:16.770
Hey, Sergeant Seo!

43:16.770 --> 43:17.700
Did he answer?

43:19.550 --> 43:21.600
Why didn't you take the calls?

43:23.570 --> 43:24.560
He's not answering.

43:25.620 --> 43:26.760
Do you want to leave a message?

43:32.090 --> 43:33.740
I'll give you one minute

43:33.740 --> 43:35.740
to use up all the ammo.

43:35.740 --> 43:37.760
Don't miss your target!

43:38.120 --> 43:38.960
Fire!

43:38.960 --> 43:39.870
Fire!

44:01.750 --> 44:04.030
There are three absolute imperatives.

44:07.250 --> 44:09.800
When you're ordered to attack,

44:10.290 --> 44:11.910
only move forward.

44:13.870 --> 44:16.540
When you're ordered to defend,

44:16.540 --> 44:17.760
never retreat.

44:18.940 --> 44:21.040
When you're ordered to stand by…

44:29.530 --> 44:30.680
You have three bullets left.

44:51.660 --> 44:53.760
When you're ordered to stand by,

44:53.950 --> 44:56.650
don't even move a muscle.

44:57.000 --> 44:59.080
That's what the absolute imperatives are all about.

44:59.080 --> 45:02.150
Orders for soldiers come before your lives.

45:02.150 --> 45:06.450
That's the duty of the Special Forces that you've chosen.

45:09.980 --> 45:10.870
Sir!

45:12.750 --> 45:13.670
It's a call from the Commander.

45:15.510 --> 45:17.340
This is the end of today's training.

45:17.750 --> 45:18.620
Dismissed!

45:18.620 --> 45:19.590
Dismissed.

45:20.090 --> 45:21.000
Are there any soldiers

45:21.000 --> 45:22.760
you can recommend for Alpha Team?

45:23.290 --> 45:24.300
I'll write a report

45:24.300 --> 45:25.790
after the five-week training session is over.

45:25.790 --> 45:28.040
The legendary instructor from hell has returned.

45:28.040 --> 45:29.290
Choose a few officers

45:29.290 --> 45:31.290
and train them to be team leaders.

45:32.420 --> 45:34.830
With this incident in Uruk, I think Yoo Shi Jin

45:34.830 --> 45:36.620
should come back and build his career

45:36.620 --> 45:39.910
at the Army Headquarters or the Ministry of Defense

45:39.910 --> 45:41.890
to build up his connections.

45:44.250 --> 45:45.060
Yes, sir!

45:46.960 --> 45:50.340
Myung Joo thought my orders regarding you

45:50.340 --> 45:51.650
are unfair.

45:51.650 --> 45:52.930
What's your point?

45:54.120 --> 45:56.400
I feel the same way as Lieutenant Yoon.

45:58.220 --> 45:59.880
I'll accept the investigation.

46:00.300 --> 46:01.620
Report me if you want.

46:01.620 --> 46:02.650
That won't happen, sir!

46:04.950 --> 46:06.280
Because I

46:06.570 --> 46:07.700
lost this fight.

46:08.590 --> 46:09.570
Yeah?

46:09.570 --> 46:12.770
You hold the weapon that I can never beat.

46:13.910 --> 46:15.510
It's sincerity.

46:17.110 --> 46:20.090
You're sincerely worried about her future,

46:20.090 --> 46:24.050
and you sincerely feel I'm not suitable for her.

46:25.710 --> 46:26.680
Unfortunately,

46:27.580 --> 46:29.950
I agree with you on the matter.

46:30.720 --> 46:32.830
That's why I can't beat you in this fight.

46:34.370 --> 46:36.200
For the lieutenant,

46:36.360 --> 46:38.050
I chose to lose.

46:48.640 --> 46:52.160
I'm writing this letter hoping

46:52.200 --> 46:54.230
that you won't be able to read it.

46:55.410 --> 46:59.230
If you're reading this letter,

46:59.230 --> 47:02.510
you and I miss each other again.

47:02.510 --> 47:06.600
That means that my father gave you an order to run away from me again.

47:09.940 --> 47:11.180
I'm sorry

47:12.100 --> 47:13.850
that I'm someone who's in your way.

47:15.840 --> 47:18.830
Yet I still ask you how you are,

47:19.970 --> 47:22.660
and you won't be able to find an answer.

47:24.080 --> 47:26.680
We're far away from each other like this.

47:30.790 --> 47:32.380
I'm sorry

47:33.230 --> 47:35.930
that I had to go where you were,

47:37.470 --> 47:39.490
even knowing this would happen.

47:42.650 --> 47:45.060
I wish I could hold your hand

47:45.060 --> 47:49.940
and hug you more.

47:50.500 --> 47:55.220
Because I still love you so much.

47:57.230 --> 47:59.620
Even if you don't ever get to read this letter.

48:00.400 --> 48:01.240
I'd rather

48:01.240 --> 48:02.900
be with you in Uruk right now.

48:04.250 --> 48:06.130
So? How did it go?

48:06.710 --> 48:08.210
Are we back together?

48:08.600 --> 48:09.810
Or

48:10.820 --> 48:12.430
are we still far apart?

48:21.050 --> 48:25.630
Excuse me. Are you the new army surgeon?

48:28.740 --> 48:29.870
An intern from Haesung Hospital?

48:30.650 --> 48:32.030
I have a baby face,

48:32.030 --> 48:33.790
but I'm in my first year of residency.

48:34.430 --> 48:36.370
Can I ask you something?

48:36.680 --> 48:38.330
I need to join the army soon.

48:39.260 --> 48:41.080
Do they give army surgeons guns?

48:41.080 --> 48:42.550
Army surgeons are still soldiers.

48:44.390 --> 48:46.500
What if a war breaks out?

48:47.010 --> 48:48.400
Do you treat the enemy soldiers?

48:48.810 --> 48:50.210
Army surgeons are still  Dr.s.

48:51.330 --> 48:52.590
So cool.

48:54.240 --> 48:56.260
Are you hitting on me?

48:56.540 --> 49:00.130
What?  Don't get me wrong.

49:00.130 --> 49:02.360
I think it's a cool dilemma

49:02.360 --> 49:04.350
that army surgeons have.

49:04.350 --> 49:06.100
Besides,

49:06.890 --> 49:08.250
you're not that pretty.

49:08.590 --> 49:10.110
I'm not?

49:12.050 --> 49:14.750
Oh my! You have an eye for women.

49:15.140 --> 49:17.610
So proud of you. We have a meeting.

49:17.610 --> 49:18.410
Okay.

49:18.410 --> 49:20.830
Look at you guys from Haesung Group.

49:21.380 --> 49:22.450
What's all that?

49:22.450 --> 49:23.410
Are you asking a question or trying to pick a fight?

49:23.410 --> 49:24.810
You're only here

49:24.810 --> 49:26.310
for 15 days to give vaccines

49:26.310 --> 49:28.890
and take a few pictures.

49:28.890 --> 49:31.660
Did you have to bring all that stuff?

49:32.100 --> 49:33.410
It's like you bought a designer brand bag to

49:33.410 --> 49:35.950
pack lunch for your child on a school picnic day.

49:37.040 --> 49:39.610
Thank you for comparing me to a designer brand bag.

49:39.660 --> 49:40.940
You're a lunch box.

49:44.280 --> 49:46.530
What you're looking at is a Medical Zone,

49:46.530 --> 49:48.770
a state-of-the art field hospital.

49:48.770 --> 49:50.100
The reason we brought all that stuff

49:50.100 --> 49:51.890
in this fifteen-day trip

49:51.890 --> 49:54.480
is because we'll donate it to the UN.

49:54.480 --> 49:56.050
Is there a problem, Lieutenant Yoon?

49:56.050 --> 49:57.700
I'm not sure if I should answer that.

49:59.040 --> 50:00.270
I'm kind of busy. Bye.

50:03.580 --> 50:05.280
What a rude woman!

50:05.280 --> 50:06.330
She can hear you.

50:06.640 --> 50:08.360
I wanted her to hear me.

50:08.880 --> 50:10.150
She's pretending she didn't.

50:12.470 --> 50:14.470
I won. Let's go.

50:16.830 --> 50:17.730
Are you sure you won?

50:18.820 --> 50:20.950
Why? Why do you think you won?

50:21.890 --> 50:23.410
Get more Bioflor

50:23.410 --> 50:24.770
and Entelon pills.

50:24.770 --> 50:27.490
Today, Ms. Ha and...

50:28.780 --> 50:30.210
Any volunteers on duty for me?

50:30.210 --> 50:31.380
No.

50:31.380 --> 50:34.140
Then I'll gladly be on duty.

50:36.780 --> 50:37.810
That's everything.

50:37.810 --> 50:39.050
Any questions?

50:42.240 --> 50:44.430
By the way, why do we have meetings here

50:44.430 --> 50:46.010
instead of the Medical Zone?

50:47.450 --> 50:49.950
Who wants to move that thing to the Medical Zone?

50:51.100 --> 50:53.140
Not me.

50:57.680 --> 50:59.290
This is Housemother B.

50:59.290 --> 51:00.750
Pretty Girl, respond. Over.

51:01.260 --> 51:03.740
This is really fun.

51:03.740 --> 51:05.840
This is Pretty Girl. Over!

51:05.840 --> 51:08.350
What's for lunch? Over!

51:08.350 --> 51:10.350
I'll check and let you know. Over!

51:12.130 --> 51:15.260
I'll let you know what today's lunch is.

51:18.000 --> 51:19.440
Can we talk? Over!

51:20.540 --> 51:21.850
Pretty Girl. See you later.

51:22.250 --> 51:23.620
See you later.

51:24.460 --> 51:25.890
Bye.

51:35.680 --> 51:36.910
What is it?

51:36.910 --> 51:38.580
Is it okay for you to talk to me like this?

51:39.400 --> 51:40.440
Why not?

51:40.440 --> 51:42.720
Your fiancée won't like it. Don't you think so?

51:43.790 --> 51:45.190
Where are you going? Let's talk.

51:45.190 --> 51:46.300
I don't want to.

51:52.670 --> 51:54.470
About Captain Yoo and Doctor Kang.

51:55.460 --> 51:57.380
There must be something between them.

51:57.380 --> 51:58.760
Like what?

51:58.760 --> 52:01.040
Like something that you and I have?

52:01.040 --> 52:03.630
What do you and I have? A grudge?

52:03.630 --> 52:04.480
A grudge?

52:07.220 --> 52:09.110
I hate Ha Ja Ae. I hate Ha Ja Ae.

52:09.110 --> 52:10.710
I hate Ha Ja Ae.

52:16.780 --> 52:18.880
What a five-year-old!

52:20.920 --> 52:22.190
Cover it.

52:22.530 --> 52:23.830
It can’t work.

52:23.830 --> 52:26.170
Don't pronounce her death yet.

52:26.170 --> 52:27.920
I'm the Dr. here.

52:31.140 --> 52:33.130
You know what?

52:33.130 --> 52:35.240
You look like a hardware store owner.

52:35.240 --> 52:38.130
I am a hardware store owner.

52:38.130 --> 52:41.740
But I find you sexier

52:41.740 --> 52:44.520
when you're holding a scalpel than a wrench.

52:47.820 --> 52:49.870
Only girls from the East think that way.

52:50.780 --> 52:53.330
In the West, girls love guys

52:53.330 --> 52:54.380
in overalls holding a wrench.

52:56.490 --> 52:58.350
That's just silly.

53:11.440 --> 53:13.180
Door. Bring me the door.

53:21.930 --> 53:23.610
This is the Space. This is the Space.

53:23.610 --> 53:26.340
NASA! Come in! NASA! Come in!

53:26.340 --> 53:28.750
Roger. This is NASA. What's going on?

53:31.540 --> 53:33.370
We have a problem with the power plant.

53:33.370 --> 53:35.990
We're running out of mosquito repellant.

53:38.200 --> 53:40.070
Calm down and hang in there.

53:42.180 --> 53:43.840
We'll send some over soon. Over.

53:43.840 --> 53:46.030
Copy that. We'll try to survive without it.

53:48.270 --> 53:49.450
Here you are.

53:55.210 --> 53:56.230
Clear!

53:59.140 --> 54:01.140
This is Fried Chicken.

54:01.140 --> 54:03.370
Are you there, Pretty Girl?

54:03.370 --> 54:08.270
Sing a song for the injured soldiers here. Over!

54:10.560 --> 54:11.980
Copy that. Over.

54:14.740 --> 54:18.220
This is Pretty Girl and I

54:18.220 --> 54:19.340
just got back from my world tour.

54:22.050 --> 54:25.710
Under the blue sky

54:25.710 --> 54:29.590
The field is full of flowers

54:29.590 --> 54:33.380
The sun has risen over

54:33.380 --> 54:37.160
The new world

54:37.160 --> 54:40.940
You and I are here to

54:40.940 --> 54:44.390
Serve our country.

54:44.810 --> 54:52.250
To obtain freedom and peace

54:52.250 --> 54:55.870
I'll sacrifice

54:55.870 --> 54:59.530
My youth and my life

55:23.440 --> 55:24.260
What's the cake for?

55:24.260 --> 55:25.340
What's the occasion?

55:25.340 --> 55:26.560
Come this way, ma'am.

55:26.890 --> 55:28.540
I was going to send someone for you.

55:28.540 --> 55:29.790
It's a going-away party.

55:30.320 --> 55:31.900
Who's leaving?

55:32.120 --> 55:33.870
It's the Captain's going-away party.

55:34.330 --> 55:36.120
Captain...

55:38.750 --> 55:40.080
Captain Yoo?

55:40.080 --> 55:41.240
Yes.

55:41.240 --> 55:43.350
Captain Yoo's leaving tomorrow.

55:49.670 --> 55:51.780
How could he leave without saying anything to me?

55:52.450 --> 55:54.300
Unbelievable!

55:56.320 --> 55:57.610
How can he do that?

56:06.930 --> 56:09.220
It's 20:30. Shift change.

56:09.220 --> 56:10.340
Keep in service.

56:11.020 --> 56:12.290
Copy that.

56:18.800 --> 56:20.980
Yoo Shi Jin, how can you do this to me?

56:20.980 --> 56:21.930
How can you do this

56:22.760 --> 56:24.270
without saying anything...

56:24.270 --> 56:25.250
This is Big Boss.

56:25.250 --> 56:26.570
Oh my!

56:26.570 --> 56:29.750
If anyone has Doctor Kang from the medical team in sight, report to me.

56:35.610 --> 56:37.580
I'm right here. What do you want?

56:37.890 --> 56:38.930
Dr. Kang?

56:39.350 --> 56:42.180
Why are you using the army channel?

56:42.180 --> 56:43.780
Are you a spy?

56:44.420 --> 56:45.570
We need to talk.

56:46.170 --> 56:47.620
Where are you?

56:51.400 --> 56:53.050
I'm going home tomorrow.

56:54.040 --> 56:55.270
I guess you already knew.

56:56.440 --> 56:57.820
Yes, I do.

56:58.790 --> 57:00.890
I'm the last one to find out

57:00.890 --> 57:03.750
out of everyone in the barracks.

57:05.050 --> 57:06.880
I was going to tell you yesterday,

57:06.880 --> 57:10.250
but you ran away. Remember?

57:11.240 --> 57:13.220
You should've stopped me.

57:13.220 --> 57:14.700
You even saved Private Ryan.

57:14.700 --> 57:16.080
You should've stopped me and told me.

57:16.080 --> 57:18.750
You're mad at me.

57:18.750 --> 57:21.070
I don't know why,

57:21.070 --> 57:22.740
but I should be happy.

57:23.770 --> 57:24.710
Am I right?

57:24.710 --> 57:25.840
You're wrong.

57:30.740 --> 57:34.790
Are you still confused?

57:43.210 --> 57:45.060
Right.

57:46.130 --> 57:48.050
Let me ask you one thing.

57:48.050 --> 57:49.900
Because this might be my last chance.

57:53.860 --> 57:54.650
When I kissed you

57:54.650 --> 57:55.580
without your permission…

57:55.580 --> 57:56.810
Can you not bring that up until...

57:56.810 --> 57:58.340
What should I do?

58:01.350 --> 58:07.380
Do you want me to apologize? Or confess?

58:48.630 --> 58:52.150
Next Episode

58:52.510 --> 58:54.390
I drank it with Dr. Kang.

58:54.390 --> 58:55.930
Did everything go well?

58:55.930 --> 58:57.880
I just miss you so much.

58:57.880 --> 58:59.130
When do you finish?

58:59.130 --> 59:00.710
Can I ask you something?

59:00.710 --> 59:02.340
Do you have feelings for Shi Jin?

59:02.340 --> 59:04.150
Where's Captain Yoo?

59:04.150 --> 59:07.080
Captain Yoo left last night.

59:07.080 --> 59:11.380
A strong 6.7 magnitude earthquake...

59:11.380 --> 59:12.800
The power plant has collapsed.

59:12.800 --> 59:16.520
We don't know who's alive from the medical team.

59:16.520 --> 59:18.110
I hate you, Yoo Shi Jin.

59:18.110 --> 59:20.050
I can't even beg you to stay.

59:20.050 --> 59:21.640
This is Captain Yoo Shi Jin from Alpha Team.

59:21.640 --> 59:24.370
Put anyone who knows the situation in Mouru through.

59:24.910 --> 59:26.730
Don't hang up and do it now!
